These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: folk, dubstep, electronic, r&b, hip-hop, reggae, country
1. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
3. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is between the fan of folk and the fan of electronic##2
5. the fan of r&b is between the fan of dubstep and the fan of folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Music-Genre   | country | electronic | hip-hop | folk | r&b | dubstep | reggae |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: magic-tricks, gardening, cooking, video-games, hiking, writing, reading
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Hobby   | writing | reading | magic-tricks | cooking | video-games | gardening | hiking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-3::.
