2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is reading##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Hobby   | board-games | rock-climbing | magic-tricks | reading | cooking | gardening | singing |

